  "text": "Skip to main contentGet Disco Elysium and five other dice-rolling titles for just $13 at HumbleShoppingDeal AlertGet Disco Elysium and five other dice-rolling titles for just $13 at HumbleThe Dice \u0026 Destiny Bundle is a collection of critically acclaimed CRPGsMar 31, 2025, 8:43 PM UTCImage: ZA/UMAlice Jovanée (she/her) is a commerce writer, and she has been writing about gaming and tech since 2005. Prior to Polygon, she worked at publications such as The Verge.A collection of six excellent story-driven titles powered by six-sided dice are currently available for just $13 on Humble. The highlight of the new Dice \u0026 Destiny bundle is the investigative RPG Disco Elysium: The Final Cut, but you’ll also receive Pillars of Eternity: Definitive Edition, Pillars of Eternity 2: Obsidian Edition, Citizen Sleeper, Broken Roads, and Roadwarden.The Pillars of Eternity franchise offers a high-fantasy, isometric CRPG experience similar to the classic Baldur’s Gate titles. And would you believe it’s still in development 10 years after release? The devs just dropped a turn-based update for the original that brings it in line with the upgraded sequel. Meanwhile, Broken Roads puts an original spin on post-apocalyptic role-playing.In addition to this collection of six other CRPGs, you’ll also get a 15% off coupon to purchase Citizen Sleeper 2 from Steam, reducing the usual $25 price to $21.25.As with other Humble bundles, a portion of each sale goes to benefit a nonprofit. In this case, part of your purchase will benefit Care.org, an organization dedicated to combating hunger and poverty around the world. You can use the “Adjust Donation” drop-down menu on the right side of the bundle page to adjust how the funds from your sale are distributed.ShopkeeperPolygon’s handpicked deals on games, movies, books, and more.See More: Deal AlertGamingShoppingCitizen Sleeper 2: Starward VectorDisco ElysiumPillars of EternityPillars of Eternity 2: Deadfire",
